Template: poppet/mysql-host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Enter MySQL Hostname [localhost]:
 Please provide the hostname for mysql server.

Template: poppet/mysql-root-pass
Type: password
Description: Enter MySQL root password:
 Please provide the password for your MySQL sever.


Template: poppet/mysql-root-user
Type: string
Default: root
Description: Enter MySQL root Username[root]:
 Please Enter your MySQL Root Username

Template: poppet/mysql-db-name
Type: string
Default: poppet
